      We may collect personal information that you provide directly to us. This includes:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Personal Identification Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and government-issued ID (as required by some hosts for verification).</li>
      <li><strong>Booking Information:</strong> Details of the properties you book, dates of stay, and any special requests.</li>
      <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Credit/debit card details or other payment information, which is processed securely by our payment partners. We do not store your full payment card details.</li>
      <li><strong>Communications:</strong> Any messages you send to us or to other users (hosts/guests) through our platform.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      We also collect some information automatically when you use our site, such as your IP address, browser type, and how you navigate the platform (pages viewed, time spent).
    </p>

