    <p>
      We use the information we collect for various purposes, including:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>To process your bookings and payments.</li>
      <li>To facilitate communication between you and the property host.</li>
      <li>To verify your identity and ensure the security of our platform.</li>
      <li>To send you booking confirmations, updates, and support messages.</li>
      <li>To improve and optimize our website and services.</li>
      <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
    </ul>

