      <li><strong>With Payment Processors:</strong> We share payment information with trusted third-party payment gateways to process your transactions securely.</li>
      <li><strong>For Legal Reasons:</strong> We may disclose your information if required by law, such as in response to a court order or subpoena.</li>
      <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> We may use third-party companies to help us operate our business (e.g., email services, customer support). These providers only have access to the information needed to perform their tasks.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      We do not sell your personal information to third parties.
